    • Field Detail

      • m_entries

        protected List<TableEntry> m_entries
        The set of entries in the table. Note that we use a list, and not a set, as we need the entries to be enumerated in the same order every time. Otherwise, the n-th "row" of the table would not always refer to the same data point.
